snippet.title: Disastory - Official Demo Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: Meet quirky characters and check out the colorful world of Disastory in this latest trailer for the upcoming illustrated choice-driven roleplaying adventure where coffee machines find love and teenage girls steal eyeballs!? In Disastory, explore a vibrant world with absurd stories and characters. A demo for Disastory is coming to Steam on January 22, 2025.
